SELECT COUNT(*)
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]

2025-05-08 20:21:56.839 +03:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__p_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_1='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [p].[Id] AS [ProductId], [s].[Name] AS [ShopName], [c].[Name] AS [CategoryName], [p].[Name] AS [ProductName], [p].[ImageUrl], [p].[Price], [p].[Color], [p].[Stock]
FROM [Products] AS [p]
INNER JOIN [Categories] AS [c] ON [p].[CategoryId] = [c].[Id]
INNER JOIN [Shops] AS [s] ON [p].[ShopId] = [s].[Id]
